  "2361770": {
    "name": "超级忍 反攻的斩击",
    "steam_appid": 2361770,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361770/extras/49dc50690af27c1f5a508ff39f6a38b0.avif?t=1772105366\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■关于本作</h2>全程手绘——精致细腻，独具匠心的艺术风格。<br>一念之间决定胜负，战斗中蕴藏精密策略与极致快感。<br>毫不留情的高难度平台跳跃挑战，考验你的操作与耐心！<br>在怒涛般的战斗与残酷的跳跃挑战中前行——你能坚持到最后，见证乔·武藏复仇的最终结局吗？<br>世嘉携手《怒之铁拳4》开发团队倾力打造，献上一场前所未有的无间断忍者动作盛宴！<br>来吧——做好觉悟，迎接挑战！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■剧情梗概</h2>在忍道中登峰造极的传说级忍者“乔·武藏”，在目睹了焚烧殆尽的故乡以及变为石头的伙伴之后，毅然踏上复仇之旅。这是为了铲除丧心病狂的极恶势力，也是为了替惨遭毒手的伙伴报仇雪恨……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361770/extras/5a165d23367ca77d1c29884f269b98fb.poster.avif?t=1772105366\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361770/extras/5a165d23367ca77d1c29884f269b98fb.webm?t=1772105366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361770/extras/5a165d23367ca77d1c29884f269b98fb.mp4?t=1772105366\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■登峰造极的忍者技艺</h2>通过护符自由拓展乔·武藏的能力，活用忍刀，手里剑，忍术以及忍法来歼灭敌人吧。根据情况从众多招式中进行选择，施展出具有自身战斗风格的多种连击。丝滑且充满动感的动画表现与速度感十足的动作相结合，带来独一无二的爽快战斗体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361770/extras/825b63294bf50e05de1885d89c3666eb.poster.avif?t=1772105366\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361770/extras/825b63294bf50e05de1885d89c3666eb.webm?t=1772105366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361770/extras/825b63294bf50e05de1885d89c3666eb.mp4?t=1772105366\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■手绘美术风格描绘的美丽世界</h2>从军事基地到炽热沙漠等丰富多彩的关卡在复仇之路上等待着乔·武藏前来探索。所有关卡都以手绘美术风格呈现，并通过细致的描绘刻画此次复仇之旅。<br>同时，旅途中也存在着需要施展各种忍技才可突破的难关，仔细探索才可发现的隐藏道路等等丰富的游戏元素，提供充满乐趣的横版动作游戏体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361770/extras/ed9d1e9611fe8128ee43ac52fada19c2.poster.avif?t=1772105366\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361770/extras/ed9d1e9611fe8128ee43ac52fada19c2.webm?t=1772105366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361770/extras/ed9d1e9611fe8128ee43ac52fada19c2.mp4?t=1772105366\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>※商品内容和规格可能会在未经通知的情况下进行更改。",
